INTENT:

The Guardian source is published openly for transparency and security review,
not for redistribution. The value of Lictor Guardian is in the hosted service
operated at lictor.ai — including monitoring, compliance evidence, alerting,
SLAs, and the operations team that runs it. Self-hosting Guardian provides
none of that value and creates no benefit for the user that the lictor.ai
hosted service does not already provide.

If you have a business need that requires self-hosting (regulated environment,
air-gapped deployment, sovereign-cloud requirement, etc.) — please contact
us at hello@lictor.ai. We're willing to discuss enterprise self-hosting
licenses on a case-by-case basis.

